OL,3,CHouseholds urged to send in energy
OL,4,Cmeter readings ahead of October 1
OL,5,Cprice hike
OL,7,FThe regulator has raised the cap from
OL,8,Fthe current #1,568 for a typical dual
OL,9,Ffuel household in England, Scotland
OL,10,Fand Wales to #1,717, or around #12 a
OL,11,Fmonth more on an average bills.
OL,13,FThe latest cap will be just 6% or #117
OL,14,Flower than it was compared to the same
OL,15,Fperiod last year.
