OL,3,CHouseholds urged to send in energy
OL,4,Cmeter readings ahead of October 1
OL,5,Cprice hike
OL,7,FThose households on a standard
OL,8,Fvariable tariff (SVT) ` as opposed to
OL,9,Fa fixed deal ` and who do not have a
OL,10,Fsmart meter should submit their
OL,11,Felectricity and gas readings to their
OL,12,Fsupplier as close as possible to
OL,13,FOctober 1 to ensure any energy they
OL,14,Fuse before this date is not
OL,15,Finaccurately billed at the higher
OL,16,Fprices.
