OL,7,FComparison site Uswitch.com calculated
OL,8,Fthat the average household on an SVT
OL,9,Fis expected to spend #135 on energy in
OL,10,FOctober compared with #55 in September
OL,11,Fdue to a combination of higher rates
OL,12,Fand increased usage at the start of
OL,13,Fautumn.
OL,15,FUswitch energy spokesman Ben Gallizzi
OL,16,Fsaid: "With energy prices rising next
OL,17,Fweek, it's vital that households
OL,18,Fsubmit a meter reading, with a #19
OL,19,Fdifference between the cost of a
OL,20,Fweek's energy at September's prices
OL,21,Fcompared with October.
