OL,7,F"Customers who don't have a smart
OL,8,Fmeter should aim to submit their
OL,9,Freadings before or on Tuesday, October
OL,10,F1, so their supplier has an updated `
OL,11,Fand accurate ` view of their account.
OL,13,F"If you delay submitting your
OL,14,Freadings, some of your September
OL,15,Fenergy usage could end up being
OL,16,Festimated and therefore charged under
OL,17,Fthe higher October rates. Try making
OL,18,Fthis task a monthly habit for billing
OL,19,Faccuracy.
