OL,7,F"Households are also advised to see
OL,8,Fwhether now is the time to change
OL,9,Ftheir energy tariff, to beat the
OL,10,FOctober price hikes.
OL,12,F"There are a number of fixed tariffs
OL,13,Fworth considering right now. By opting
OL,14,Ffor a fixed deal, you're locking in
OL,15,Fthose rates for the duration ` usually
OL,16,F12 months ` which means households
OL,17,Fcould have price certainty and avoid
OL,18,Fthe ups and downs of the price cap."
